 like =E2=80=9Cwell yes this sounds like wire fraud=E2=80=9D and convict th=
em. Seriously the chats are bad!Two former Deutsche Bank AG traders named=
=C2=A0Matthew Connolly and Gavin Black were convicted in a New York federal=
