=A0All three cooperators testified that they never contemporaneously told a=
nyone that they thought the=C2=A0practice was wrong.But at trial Connolly a=
nd Black said, well, but you haven=E2=80=99t proven that the=C2=A0actual ra=
tes they submitted=C2=A0were wrong. Maybe Deutsche Bank could have borrowed=
