s, were you to do so by asking for and then accepting inter-bank offers in =
reasonable market size just prior to 11 a.m. London time,=E2=80=9D and Deut=
sche Bank=C2=A0had said =E2=80=9C0.525%,=E2=80=9D and=C2=A0it could in fact=
