heir order placement on an app.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Prices are =
similar to grocery stores, discounts are plentiful, and many services don=
=E2=80=99t have a fee or minimum order, allowing consumers to request a sin=
gle pint of Ben &amp; Jerry=E2=80=99s delivered to their doorstep. Food-del=
ivery app DoorDash Inc., based in San Francisco, also recently entered the =
fray in New York City.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">While these consumer=
